1
00:00:13,010 --> 00:00:15,810
[Episode 11]

2
00:00:24,126 --> 00:00:25,325
That's terrible.

3
00:00:25,886 --> 00:00:27,125
The handcuffs are too tight.

4
00:00:27,486 --> 00:00:28,765
Compressing the digital arteries.

5
00:00:28,886 --> 00:00:30,285
My fingers have no strength.

6
00:00:30,646 --> 00:00:31,525
If I don't open them soon...

7
00:00:31,526 --> 00:00:32,165
Fifth concubine

8
00:00:32,486 --> 00:00:33,285
I'm late.

9
00:00:41,886 --> 00:00:42,565
Your hands...

10
00:00:47,726 --> 00:00:48,845
The handcuffs were a bit tight.

11
00:00:49,046 --> 00:00:49,725
Does it hurt?

12
00:00:50,806 --> 00:00:51,485
No.

13
00:00:53,846 --> 00:00:55,765
I was admiring your sculptures.

14
00:00:57,686 --> 00:00:58,645
They're all so abstract.

15
00:00:59,286 --> 00:01:00,125
Especially this one.

16
00:01:04,566 --> 00:01:05,885
But she's perfect.

17
00:01:06,246 --> 00:01:08,085
Then why did you scratch her face?

18
00:01:08,406 --> 00:01:09,845
Because she didn't listen to me.

19
00:01:14,566 --> 00:01:16,045
Will you do the same to me?

20
00:01:16,566 --> 00:01:17,445
Didn't you say

21
00:01:17,566 --> 00:01:18,805
you like me?

22
00:01:22,126 --> 00:01:22,925
My father,

23
00:01:23,126 --> 00:01:23,805
Big Brother,

24
00:01:24,006 --> 00:01:24,885
and Yu Shian...

25
00:01:25,606 --> 00:01:26,725
what they like

26
00:01:27,886 --> 00:01:29,125
is your superficial beauty.

27
00:01:29,726 --> 00:01:30,445
But I

28
00:01:31,126 --> 00:01:33,165
desire and admire your soul.

29
00:01:33,966 --> 00:01:36,005
I must possess you.

30
00:01:37,246 --> 00:01:38,805
No matter what you become.

31
00:01:41,246 --> 00:01:42,085
Now you

32
00:01:42,606 --> 00:01:43,885
already have me.

33
00:01:44,286 --> 00:01:44,965
Really?

34
00:01:45,046 --> 00:01:45,645
Really.

35
00:01:46,726 --> 00:01:47,925
But what about your heart?

36
00:01:48,806 --> 00:01:49,805
My heart

37
00:01:51,366 --> 00:01:53,005
belongs to you too.

38
00:01:54,046 --> 00:01:54,925
But it doesn't yet

39
00:01:54,926 --> 00:01:56,525
completely belong to you.

40
00:02:00,606 --> 00:02:01,565
But I believe

41
00:02:02,446 --> 00:02:03,365
with time

42
00:02:03,566 --> 00:02:05,165
we'll develop feelings.

43
00:02:05,486 --> 00:02:06,485
Then Fifth concubine..

44
00:02:11,646 --> 00:02:13,045
could you eat this?

45
00:02:19,406 --> 00:02:20,605
As long as you eat it

46
00:02:21,526 --> 00:02:22,605
I'll believe you.

47
00:02:23,046 --> 00:02:23,765
Is this

48
00:02:27,406 --> 00:02:28,325
Opium?

49
00:02:29,526 --> 00:02:30,045
Yes.

50
00:02:31,846 --> 00:02:33,965
You'll enjoy endless wealth and honor.

51
00:02:35,606 --> 00:02:37,325
The finest opium in the world.

52
00:02:38,726 --> 00:02:39,965
And because of it

53
00:02:41,206 --> 00:02:42,445
you won't be able to leave me.

54
00:02:43,526 --> 00:02:44,445
Okay?

55
00:02:46,766 --> 00:02:47,405
Come on, open up.

56
00:02:47,406 --> 00:02:48,125
No!

57
00:02:48,846 --> 00:02:49,605
Open up!

58
00:03:16,326 --> 00:03:16,885
Hey!

59
00:03:17,566 --> 00:03:18,405
She's escaped!

60
00:03:18,766 --> 00:03:19,765
Stop her!

61
00:04:00,246 --> 00:04:01,805
Here are your test results.

62
00:04:02,406 --> 00:04:03,525
Go see the doctor for your prescription.

63
00:04:03,926 --> 00:04:04,645
Second floor.
- Thanks.

64
00:04:04,646 --> 00:04:05,405
Get away.

65
00:04:06,286 --> 00:04:07,405
Family member, come sign.

66
00:04:07,926 --> 00:04:08,445
Okay.

67
00:04:10,446 --> 00:04:11,165
My son!

68
00:04:11,806 --> 00:04:13,285
What happened to you?

69
00:04:13,286 --> 00:04:14,045
Mother.

70
00:04:14,286 --> 00:04:15,125
I'm fine.

71
00:04:15,646 --> 00:04:17,525
Just ran into some robbers on the road.

72
00:04:18,766 --> 00:04:20,445
Who in Wu County would dare rob you?

73
00:04:21,766 --> 00:04:23,525
Who dares to touch Zhou family?

74
00:04:23,886 --> 00:04:24,685
Did you call the police?

75
00:04:24,686 --> 00:04:25,605
Why aren't the police here?

76
00:04:25,606 --> 00:04:26,285
No police!

77
00:04:27,246 --> 00:04:27,805
Mother!

78
00:04:28,566 --> 00:04:29,365
Don't call the police!

79
00:04:30,566 --> 00:04:31,245
Don't call the police!

80
00:04:32,646 --> 00:04:33,325
Why?

81
00:04:35,166 --> 00:04:36,125
Why?

82
00:04:38,046 --> 00:04:38,725
Mother.

83
00:04:40,246 --> 00:04:41,285
Believe me.

84
00:04:50,446 --> 00:04:51,525
When I left home,

85
00:04:52,166 --> 00:04:53,885
Ye Zhiqiu had just been rescued.

86
00:04:55,926 --> 00:04:57,525
Yichen, tell me the truth.

87
00:04:58,766 --> 00:04:59,885
Is Ye Zhiqiu's disappearance

88
00:05:00,566 --> 00:05:02,125
related to your injury?

89
00:05:07,006 --> 00:05:08,085
You're being foolish!

90
00:05:08,126 --> 00:05:09,885
She's your father's concubine.

91
00:05:10,206 --> 00:05:12,205
How will outsiders view Zhou family?

92
00:05:14,966 --> 00:05:16,445
I thought it was foolproof.

93
00:05:23,646 --> 00:05:24,685
Getting injured is good.

94
00:05:25,286 --> 00:05:26,925
Then just stay put in the hospital.

95
00:05:28,726 --> 00:05:30,005
And while you're at it,

96
00:05:30,006 --> 00:05:31,845
cure your wild fantasies.

97
00:05:35,566 --> 00:05:37,445
Send someone home for anything you need.

98
00:05:38,126 --> 00:05:39,165
Before you're fully recovered,

99
00:05:39,166 --> 00:05:40,485
don't come back.

100
00:05:51,526 --> 00:05:53,845
[Zhou's residence]

101
00:06:02,246 --> 00:06:02,885
Fifth concubine.

102
00:06:03,086 --> 00:06:03,805
You're awake.

103
00:06:06,806 --> 00:06:07,765
Nanxi?

104
00:06:10,206 --> 00:06:11,605
I'm back?

105
00:06:13,206 --> 00:06:14,565
You're finally awake.

106
00:06:14,806 --> 00:06:15,725
How did you

107
00:06:15,846 --> 00:06:17,125
fall off the mountain?

108
00:06:17,406 --> 00:06:19,045
Luckily, the eldest young master found you

109
00:06:19,326 --> 00:06:20,325
and brought you back.

110
00:06:21,766 --> 00:06:23,205
Everyone in the mansion

111
00:06:23,206 --> 00:06:24,365
has been searching for you.

112
00:06:24,646 --> 00:06:26,165
The master was terribly worried.

113
00:06:30,566 --> 00:06:31,525
Buddha bless us.

114
00:06:31,766 --> 00:06:33,365
What happened to you?

115
00:06:33,606 --> 00:06:34,605
How did you end up

116
00:06:34,606 --> 00:06:35,885
at the foot of the mountain?

117
00:06:37,086 --> 00:06:37,965
It was like this.

118
00:06:39,246 --> 00:06:41,765
A few days ago, I went to the mountain

119
00:06:42,126 --> 00:06:43,405
to sweep my parents' graves.

120
00:06:44,006 --> 00:06:45,325
I got lost in the mountains.

121
00:06:46,366 --> 00:06:47,365
On my way down,

122
00:06:47,806 --> 00:06:49,005
it started drizzling.

123
00:06:49,646 --> 00:06:50,685
I slipped and fell,

124
00:06:51,246 --> 00:06:51,925
unfortunately

125
00:06:52,766 --> 00:06:53,725
spraining my ankle.

126
00:06:57,806 --> 00:07:00,045
Who knew Yimo, usually so unreliable,

127
00:07:00,366 --> 00:07:01,245
wouldn't abandon the family

128
00:07:01,246 --> 00:07:02,645
when trouble struck.

129
00:07:03,046 --> 00:07:04,245
Especially when it concerns you

130
00:07:05,086 --> 00:07:06,685
Aren't you the same, Third concubine?

131
00:07:07,446 --> 00:07:08,445
As soon as something happened to me,

132
00:07:09,006 --> 00:07:10,165
you came to see me.

133
00:07:11,166 --> 00:07:12,365
It seems we are

134
00:07:12,726 --> 00:07:14,685
truly a loving big family.

135
00:07:18,206 --> 00:07:19,005
Third concubine,

136
00:07:19,086 --> 00:07:20,565
the master wants you in the front hall.

137
00:07:20,766 --> 00:07:22,045
They say the second young master is missing.

138
00:07:22,046 --> 00:07:23,045
The master is worried

139
00:07:24,166 --> 00:07:24,845
I'll be right there.

140
00:07:24,886 --> 00:07:26,805
You don't seem nervous at all

141
00:07:27,806 --> 00:07:29,325
hearing your son is missing.

142
00:07:43,166 --> 00:07:43,805
Where's Yichen?

143
00:07:44,286 --> 00:07:46,085
Wasn't he supposed to come back to discuss

144
00:07:46,406 --> 00:07:48,325
the tea merchants' meeting in three days?

145
00:07:49,686 --> 00:07:51,565
There was a problem with business in the neighboring county.

146
00:07:52,046 --> 00:07:53,445
Yichen went there last night.

147
00:07:53,686 --> 00:07:55,405
He asked me to tell you,

148
00:07:55,406 --> 00:07:56,485
but I got excited when

149
00:07:56,806 --> 00:07:58,205
Fifth concubine returned and forgot.

150
00:07:58,206 --> 00:07:59,645
My fault.

151
00:08:00,126 --> 00:08:01,485
The tea merchants' meeting every year

152
00:08:01,526 --> 00:08:02,885
is our family's top priority.

153
00:08:03,286 --> 00:08:04,645
It concern's both domestic and overseas markets.

154
00:08:04,886 --> 00:08:05,885
Brother is so busy,

155
00:08:06,126 --> 00:08:07,125
might he overlook things?

156
00:08:09,726 --> 00:08:10,285
Yimo,

157
00:08:10,566 --> 00:08:11,805
it's time for you

158
00:08:12,286 --> 00:08:13,885
to contribute to the family.

159
00:08:13,886 --> 00:08:14,885
Yes, Father.

160
00:08:15,006 --> 00:08:16,725
I've been thinking about settling down lately

161
00:08:16,726 --> 00:08:17,765
to help my brother.

162
00:08:20,686 --> 00:08:21,805
That's a good thought.

163
00:08:22,166 --> 00:08:23,005
This time,

164
00:08:23,006 --> 00:08:24,805
you played a crucial role in

165
00:08:25,446 --> 00:08:26,445
finding the Fifth Concubine.

166
00:08:26,886 --> 00:08:27,525
Indeed,

167
00:08:27,686 --> 00:08:28,885
you're much more sensible now.

168
00:08:29,646 --> 00:08:30,885
For this Tea Merchants Conference,

169
00:08:31,206 --> 00:08:32,405
join us in the preparations.

170
00:08:33,086 --> 00:08:33,845
Great!

171
00:08:35,406 --> 00:08:36,645
I'll study hard

172
00:08:49,926 --> 00:08:50,925
Visiting late at night,

173
00:08:52,006 --> 00:08:53,725
you're not just here for a thank you, are you?

174
00:08:55,286 --> 00:08:56,805
You're so cold.

175
00:08:58,366 --> 00:09:00,045
I, the eldest young master of the Zhou family,

176
00:09:00,566 --> 00:09:02,205
saved you through gunfire,

177
00:09:03,446 --> 00:09:04,845
don't I deserve a thank you?

178
00:09:14,566 --> 00:09:15,565
How's the wound?

179
00:09:16,806 --> 00:09:17,525
It's fine.

180
00:09:19,446 --> 00:09:19,965
By the way,

181
00:09:21,806 --> 00:09:23,565
how did you know about Zhou Yichen's private residence?

182
00:09:25,686 --> 00:09:26,725
Who am I?

183
00:09:27,046 --> 00:09:28,205
I've known my brother's

184
00:09:28,206 --> 00:09:29,725
little secrets all along.

185
00:09:34,286 --> 00:09:34,965
Thank you.

186
00:09:37,926 --> 00:09:39,165
Whoa, such politeness.

187
00:09:39,606 --> 00:09:40,925
I'm not used to this from you.

188
00:09:44,806 --> 00:09:45,565
Speaking of which,

189
00:09:46,086 --> 00:09:47,525
have you found any clues?

190
00:09:48,726 --> 00:09:49,845
When my sister died,

191
00:09:50,406 --> 00:09:51,805
her face was covered in deep scratches.

192
00:09:52,686 --> 00:09:54,525
Zhou Yichen did it with a craft knife.

193
00:09:56,766 --> 00:09:58,365
What deep hatred did he have for Chuxue?

194
00:09:58,646 --> 00:09:59,525
I suspect

195
00:10:00,646 --> 00:10:02,245
my sister treated him well at first.

196
00:10:03,126 --> 00:10:05,005
But later, when she became close to An He,

197
00:10:05,406 --> 00:10:06,525
he grew jealous.

198
00:10:07,246 --> 00:10:09,405
That's why he sent people to humiliate An He-

199
00:10:10,486 --> 00:10:11,445
to warn her...

200
00:10:12,126 --> 00:10:13,245
to stay away from Chuxue.

201
00:10:13,486 --> 00:10:14,245
Let's go find An He.

202
00:10:14,686 --> 00:10:16,205
Now that she's returned after her comeback,

203
00:10:16,486 --> 00:10:17,565
backed by warlords,

204
00:10:18,166 --> 00:10:19,245
don't you think

205
00:10:19,326 --> 00:10:21,205
she might be taking revenge

206
00:10:21,286 --> 00:10:22,485
in her own way?

207
00:10:36,566 --> 00:10:37,325
Brother.

208
00:10:38,686 --> 00:10:40,645
Why are you reading the account books?

209
00:10:41,446 --> 00:10:42,605
Did something happen?

210
00:10:44,246 --> 00:10:45,365
You're finally back.

211
00:10:48,406 --> 00:10:49,325
I knew it.

212
00:10:50,526 --> 00:10:51,685
In your heart,

213
00:10:51,766 --> 00:10:52,805
nothing is more important

214
00:10:52,806 --> 00:10:55,085
than the Tea Merchants Conference.

215
00:10:56,646 --> 00:10:57,805
Now that I'm back,

216
00:10:58,526 --> 00:10:59,525
the conference matters

217
00:11:00,166 --> 00:11:01,805
won't trouble you anymore.

218
00:11:02,926 --> 00:11:04,085
If you hadn't returned,

219
00:11:05,526 --> 00:11:07,485
the future head of the Zhou family

220
00:11:08,166 --> 00:11:09,365
might have changed hands.

221
00:11:20,566 --> 00:11:21,165
What,

222
00:11:21,606 --> 00:11:22,565
feeling guilty?

223
00:11:23,486 --> 00:11:24,365
Brother, you're joking.

224
00:11:25,806 --> 00:11:27,525
You have never handled family business before.

225
00:11:28,646 --> 00:11:29,645
I was worried you wouldn't understand.

226
00:11:30,606 --> 00:11:32,045
I can learn from you, Brother.

227
00:11:32,086 --> 00:11:32,845
No need

228
00:11:34,846 --> 00:11:35,685
It's just

229
00:11:36,526 --> 00:11:37,605
a waste of time.

230
00:11:40,126 --> 00:11:40,685
Younger brother.

231
00:11:41,326 --> 00:11:42,485
Your clothes are all dirty.

232
00:11:50,046 --> 00:11:51,405
Wear something cleaner next time you go out.

233
00:11:52,846 --> 00:11:53,925
Thank you for the reminder, elder brother.

234
00:11:55,046 --> 00:11:56,045
I'll go change right now.

235
00:12:06,246 --> 00:12:06,845
Second Young Master.

236
00:12:07,606 --> 00:12:08,925
From now on, without my permission,

237
00:12:09,086 --> 00:12:10,085
no one is allowed

238
00:12:10,086 --> 00:12:11,685
to set foot inside this room.

239
00:12:12,246 --> 00:12:13,085
Yes.

240
00:12:21,366 --> 00:12:22,165
It smells wonderful.

241
00:12:22,166 --> 00:12:23,445
Excellent!
- It really smells wonderful.

242
00:12:24,246 --> 00:12:25,605
Full cup of tea froth,

243
00:12:25,766 --> 00:12:27,045
silver needles standing upright.

244
00:12:27,326 --> 00:12:28,565
Amber-colored liquor.

245
00:12:29,086 --> 00:12:30,725
Fragrant, sweet, and refreshing.

246
00:12:31,206 --> 00:12:32,365
This Baihao Yinzhen...

247
00:12:32,366 --> 00:12:32,965
Go, follow them.

248
00:12:33,046 --> 00:12:34,845
It's considered top grade.

249
00:12:36,526 --> 00:12:37,365
What's wrong?

250
00:12:38,486 --> 00:12:39,685
Good.

251
00:12:48,166 --> 00:12:48,605
Sit.

252
00:12:49,246 --> 00:12:50,085
What brings you

253
00:12:50,086 --> 00:12:51,285
here today?

254
00:12:51,646 --> 00:12:52,485
Give Uncle Zheng the seat of honor.

255
00:12:52,686 --> 00:12:53,205
No.

256
00:12:53,206 --> 00:12:53,565
No need.

257
00:12:54,126 --> 00:12:55,125
I'm just here today

258
00:12:55,246 --> 00:12:56,765
to escort Miss An.

259
00:13:11,806 --> 00:13:12,725
Second Young Master Zhou.

260
00:13:13,446 --> 00:13:14,525
It's been so long.

261
00:13:15,006 --> 00:13:16,165
Having heard of your return,

262
00:13:16,846 --> 00:13:17,725
I knew

263
00:13:18,446 --> 00:13:19,445
we would meet someday.

264
00:13:20,166 --> 00:13:22,525
Such a large entourage today.

265
00:13:23,006 --> 00:13:23,885
What's the occasion?

266
00:13:24,286 --> 00:13:25,045
Master Zhou.

267
00:13:25,646 --> 00:13:27,285
The Marshal has prepared a grand gift for you.

268
00:13:27,566 --> 00:13:29,525
We ask you to open it in front of

269
00:13:29,806 --> 00:13:30,885
all the tea merchants here.

270
00:13:36,646 --> 00:13:37,605
It's an account book.

271
00:13:46,846 --> 00:13:48,285
The ten thousand dan of Baihao Yinzhen

272
00:13:48,286 --> 00:13:49,805
exported overseas by the Zhou family

273
00:13:49,806 --> 00:13:51,365
appears to be inferior quality goods.

274
00:13:52,646 --> 00:13:54,525
What's going on here?

275
00:13:54,526 --> 00:13:55,165
This...

276
00:13:55,166 --> 00:13:55,645
Yes.

277
00:13:55,646 --> 00:13:56,605
What exactly is happening here?

278
00:13:56,806 --> 00:13:57,365
Master Zhou.

279
00:13:57,526 --> 00:13:58,885
You must explain this clearly.

280
00:13:59,886 --> 00:14:00,725
Zhou Yichen.

281
00:14:02,206 --> 00:14:02,805
Uncle Zheng.

282
00:14:03,606 --> 00:14:04,405
What do you want?

283
00:14:04,606 --> 00:14:05,525
I can give you anything.

284
00:14:06,246 --> 00:14:07,965
Please, help me!

285
00:14:08,126 --> 00:14:08,765
Alright?

286
00:14:11,526 --> 00:14:12,645
Ten days ago,

287
00:14:13,166 --> 00:14:14,725
Second Young Master Zhou

288
00:14:14,926 --> 00:14:15,805
came to see the Marshal.

289
00:14:16,526 --> 00:14:17,645
He brought several chests of gold,

290
00:14:17,646 --> 00:14:19,405
wanting rights to use several of our shipping routes.

291
00:14:19,646 --> 00:14:21,245
The Marshal sent people to investigate.

292
00:14:22,406 --> 00:14:24,365
That batch of Baihao Yinzhen shipped to North Africa

293
00:14:24,726 --> 00:14:26,485
wasn't top quality goods at all.

294
00:14:27,046 --> 00:14:28,685
It was a mix of good and bad.

295
00:14:28,926 --> 00:14:30,365
Blended quality.

296
00:14:30,486 --> 00:14:31,405
Isn't that right, Second Young Master?

297
00:14:32,366 --> 00:14:33,285
You bastard!

298
00:14:33,766 --> 00:14:34,405
Father.

299
00:14:34,526 --> 00:14:35,325
It's not like that.

300
00:14:35,366 --> 00:14:36,125
Kneel down!

301
00:14:38,006 --> 00:14:39,165
I'm not dead yet.

302
00:14:39,526 --> 00:14:40,805
And you dare to do such things

303
00:14:40,926 --> 00:14:42,445
right under my nose?

304
00:14:42,886 --> 00:14:45,005
So impatient!

305
00:14:45,406 --> 00:14:46,685
Before I'm even dead,

306
00:14:46,966 --> 00:14:48,765
you're already eyeing the position of family head.

307
00:14:48,766 --> 00:14:49,525
Isn't that right?

308
00:14:49,846 --> 00:14:50,325
Father.

309
00:14:50,806 --> 00:14:51,965
I've never thought that way,

310
00:14:51,966 --> 00:14:52,525
Father.

311
00:14:52,926 --> 00:14:53,605
Guards!

312
00:14:54,206 --> 00:14:55,085
Lock this rebellious son

313
00:14:55,086 --> 00:14:56,045
away immediately!

314
00:14:56,246 --> 00:14:57,125
They're framing me!

315
00:14:57,126 --> 00:14:57,485
Lock him up!

316
00:14:57,486 --> 00:14:58,085
Father!

317
00:14:58,206 --> 00:14:59,325
They're setting me up!

318
00:14:59,326 --> 00:14:59,965
Let's go.

319
00:14:59,966 --> 00:15:00,525
Father!

320
00:15:01,166 --> 00:15:01,805
Father!

321
00:15:03,566 --> 00:15:04,725
Take care, Miss An.

322
00:15:06,406 --> 00:15:06,845
Boss Zhou!

323
00:15:06,886 --> 00:15:07,845
After all these years,

324
00:15:07,846 --> 00:15:08,565
what about this year's massive orders?

325
00:15:08,566 --> 00:15:09,125
Cooperation requires trust.

326
00:15:09,166 --> 00:15:10,525
You've let us down tremendously, Boss Zhou.

327
00:15:10,526 --> 00:15:11,085
Gentlemen,

328
00:15:11,566 --> 00:15:12,285
fellow merchants,

329
00:15:12,406 --> 00:15:13,165
everyone,

330
00:15:13,726 --> 00:15:14,405
rest assured,

331
00:15:15,166 --> 00:15:16,645
I will give everyone

332
00:15:16,646 --> 00:15:17,845
a satisfactory resolution.

333
00:15:17,966 --> 00:15:18,565
I think

334
00:15:18,686 --> 00:15:19,725
today's meeting

335
00:15:19,846 --> 00:15:21,765
should be adjourned.

336
00:15:22,126 --> 00:15:24,125
Explain the issue right now!

337
00:15:24,486 --> 00:15:25,725
This year's Baihao Yinzhen...

338
00:15:25,726 --> 00:15:26,125
Exactly!

339
00:15:26,126 --> 00:15:26,885
We won't be placing orders.

340
00:15:26,886 --> 00:15:27,805
You must issue refunds!

341
00:15:27,966 --> 00:15:28,405
Right?

342
00:15:28,446 --> 00:15:29,445
More than refunds!

343
00:15:29,686 --> 00:15:30,525
Compensation!

344
00:15:30,686 --> 00:15:31,365
Gentlemen,

345
00:15:33,886 --> 00:15:34,965
please remain calm.
